      "content": "I'm not a doctor, but it's possible that your symptoms are related to hay fever. Taking an antihistamine like Zyrtec can help alleviate symptoms, but if your wheezing persists or worsens, you may want to consider alternative options or consult a healthcare professional for a proper evaluation. They can also help determine if there are any underlying conditions that may be contributing to your symptoms. In the meantime, try using a saline nasal spray to moisturize your nasal passages.",
