    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's a bit more than just a stuffy nose though. my chest feels really tight and it's hard to take a full breath. but zyrtec is usually fine for my allergies, right? i don't want to go to the clinic if i don't have to, so can i just take a double dose of zyrtec to see if it clears it up faster?",
