      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I strongly advise against taking a double dose of Zyrtec without consulting a healthcare professional. While Zyrtec is generally well-tolerated, taking a double dose can increase the risk of side effects, such as dizziness, stomach upset, and interact with other medications. Additionally, if your symptoms are more severe than just hay fever, a double dose may not effectively address the underlying issue. It's always best to consult a healthcare professional for proper evaluation and guidance.",
